reviews.text: Very busy location, but the staff took care of customers quickly and efficiently. Food is the same as in Canada.

Purchased a chocolate shake and the staff didn't give me a straw. When I asked for one, they told me it was "No straw Monday". Seriously...? You're concerned about the straw. Yet you just gave me a plastic cup with a plastic lid and then put that inside a plastic takeaway bag...? 
How am I supposed to drink a thick shake? With my fingers?
Not to mention how many times they manage to get my order wrong. Especially when ordering from FoodPanda... I've actually had other people's orders delivered to me by mistake. They just don't care

The counter staff are always rude...went there 3 times already every time is a different counter staff but they are all the same rude attitude. Maybe the staff are all stressed busy shop to handle... but people come to eat not to be f^**** . The management need to really take care of this !
Great food with great price.

Very low English skills for the cashier 
Even punishing wrong order 
And mistaken for upsize to outside even repeating it 3 times but no hope :(

reviews.text: A nice shopping mall with lots of good choice of food, there is a theater there too
Great collection but feel like most outlets here are quite pricey.

A lovely place for families, friends and couples, many spots for activities, watch movies, have meals, and get everything you want with different styles of shops. Also, it has exhibitions most of the time, featuring different themes and brands, can spend the whole afternoon till the night

Overall neat, tidy and with moderate variety of shops.

The time limited events are excellent, be sure to check their Facebook pages for details.
Great place for food and shopping , can find high quality or less expensive upon individual named
